    always @(posedge clk) begin
        if (we && rd_addr != 5'd0)
            regs[rd_addr] <= rd_data;
    end
endmodule

## 7. Byte-Enable Logic for Stores

A `SB` writing to address 0x5 must only enable byte lane 1 of the word at 0x4:
```verilog
case (addr[1:0])
