    2'b01: be = 4'b0010;
    2'b10: be = 4'b0100;
    2'b11: be = 4'b1000;
endcase
```

## 10. Synchronous Reset Convention

Prefer synchronous reset for FPGA/ASIC portability:
```verilog
always @(posedge clk) begin
    if (rst)
        state <= 0;
    else
